      <section eId="sec_609_A">
        <num>609-A</num>
        <heading>Capital acquisition fund</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_609_A__subsec_i">
          <num>(i)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the amounts specified pursuant to subdivision three-a of section\nfive hundred thirty-two of this chapter; and (ii) contributions from the\ncorporation's pari-mutuel wagering pools, subject to the following\nlimitations:\n</p>
          </content>
          <paragraph eId="sec_609_A__subsec_i__subsec_1">
            <num>(1)</num>
            <content>
              <p>no contribution shall exceed the amount of one percent of the\ntotal pari-mutuel wagering pools for the quarter in which the\ncontribution is made;\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_609_A__subsec_i__subsec_2">
            <num>(2)</num>
            <content>
              <p>no contribution shall reduce the amount of quarterly net revenues,\nexclusive of surcharge revenues, to an amount less than fifty percent of\nsuch net revenues; and\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="sec_609_A__subsec_i__subsec_3">
            <num>(3)</num>
            <content>
              <p>the balance of the fund shall not exceed the lesser of one percent\nof total pari-mutuel wagering pools for the previous twelve months or\nthe undepreciated value of the corporation's offices, facilities and\npremises.\n</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
        </subsection>
      </section>
